{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1039,"text":"Right now"},{"time":2797,"text":"there is an aspiring teacher"},{"time":5539,"text":"who is working on a 60-page paper"},{"time":9190,"text":"based on some age-old education theory"},{"time":12700,"text":"developed by some dead education professor"},{"time":16893,"text":"wondering to herself what this task"},{"time":19611,"text":"that she's engaging in"},{"time":21251,"text":"has to do with what she wants to do with her life,"},{"time":23779,"text":"which is be an educator,"},{"time":26005,"text":"change lives, and spark magic."},{"time":30119,"text":"Right now there is an aspiring teacher"},{"time":35003,"text":"in a graduate school of education"},{"time":36959,"text":"who is watching a professor babble on and on"},{"time":39967,"text":"about engagement"},{"time":42091,"text":"in the most disengaging way possible."},{"time":47265,"text":"Right now"},{"time":48915,"text":"there's a first-year teacher at home"},{"time":51114,"text":"who is pouring through lesson plans"},{"time":53666,"text":"trying to make sense of standards,"},{"time":55996,"text":"who is trying to make sense of how\nto grade students appropriately,"},{"time":59186,"text":"while at the same time saying to herself"},{"time":60825,"text":"over and over again,"},{"time":63039,"text":"\"Don't smile till November,\""},{"time":64997,"text":"because that's what she was taught"},{"time":67080,"text":"in her teacher education program."},{"time":70102,"text":"Right now there's a student"},{"time":72958,"text":"who is coming up with a way"},{"time":74642,"text":"to convince his mom or dad"},{"time":77130,"text":"that he's very, very sick"},{"time":78638,"text":"and can't make it to school tomorrow."},{"time":82511,"text":"On the other hand, right now"},{"time":85408,"text":"there are amazing educators"},{"time":87758,"text":"that are sharing information,"},{"time":89532,"text":"information that is shared in such a beautiful way"},{"time":92179,"text":"that the students are sitting\nat the edge of their seats"},{"time":94570,"text":"just waiting for a bead of sweat"},{"time":96682,"text":"to drop off the face of this person"},{"time":99267,"text":"so they can soak up all that knowledge."},{"time":102312,"text":"Right now there is also a person"},{"time":106030,"text":"who has an entire audience rapt with attention,"},{"time":109391,"text":"a person that is weaving a powerful narrative"},{"time":112283,"text":"about a world"},{"time":113959,"text":"that the people who are listening"},{"time":115514,"text":"have never imagined or seen before,"},{"time":117880,"text":"but if they close their eyes tightly enough,"},{"time":120398,"text":"they can envision that world"},{"time":122037,"text":"because the storytelling is so compelling."},{"time":126032,"text":"Right now there's a person who can tell an audience"},{"time":129171,"text":"to put their hands up in the air"},{"time":131074,"text":"and they will stay there till he says,"},{"time":132724,"text":"\"Put them down.\""},{"time":134468,"text":"Right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136136,"text":"So people will then say,"},{"time":137540,"text":"\"Well, Chris, you describe the guy"},{"time":140403,"text":"who is going through some awful training"},{"time":142427,"text":"but you're also describing these powerful educators."},{"time":144960,"text":"If you're thinking about the world of education"},{"time":146494,"text":"or urban education in particular,"},{"time":148092,"text":"these guys will probably cancel each other out,"},{"time":150138,"text":"and then we'll be okay.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":152384,"text":"The reality is, the folks I described"},{"time":154886,"text":"as the master teachers,"},{"time":156602,"text":"the master narrative builders,"},{"time":158939,"text":"the master storytellers"},{"time":160890,"text":"are far removed from classrooms."},{"time":164488,"text":"The folks who know the skills about how to teach"},{"time":166870,"text":"and engage an audience"},{"time":168192,"text":"don't even know what teacher certification means."},{"time":171112,"text":"They may not even have the degrees"},{"time":173174,"text":"to be able to have anything"},{"time":176435,"text":"to call an education."},{"time":178739,"text":"And that to me is sad."},{"time":180471,"text":"It's sad because the people who I described,"},{"time":183470,"text":"they were very disinterested in the learning process,"},{"time":186237,"text":"want to be effective teachers,"},{"time":188095,"text":"but they have no models."},{"time":189447,"text":"I'm going to paraphrase Mark Twain."},{"time":191192,"text":"Mark Twain says that proper preparation,"},{"time":193722,"text":"or teaching,"},{"time":195122,"text":"is so powerful that it can turn bad morals to good,"},{"time":198738,"text":"it can turn awful practices into powerful ones,"},{"time":201410,"text":"it can change men and transform them"},{"time":203994,"text":"into angels."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206595,"text":"The folks who I described earlier"},{"time":208898,"text":"got proper preparation in teaching,"},{"time":210888,"text":"not in any college or university,"},{"time":212972,"text":"but by virtue of just being in the\nsame spaces of those who engage."},{"time":216967,"text":"Guess where those places are?"},{"time":219210,"text":"Barber shops,"},{"time":221276,"text":"rap concerts, and most importantly,"},{"time":224464,"text":"in the black church."},{"time":226112,"text":"And I've been framing this idea\ncalled Pentecostal pedagogy."},{"time":229031,"text":"Who here has been to a black church?"},{"time":231341,"text":"We got a couple of hands."},{"time":233650,"text":"You go to a black church,"},{"time":235013,"text":"their preacher starts off"},{"time":236624,"text":"and he realizes that he has to engage the audience,"},{"time":239510,"text":"so he starts off with this sort of wordplay"},{"time":241356,"text":"in the beginning oftentimes,"},{"time":243040,"text":"and then he takes a pause,"},{"time":244858,"text":"and he says, \"Oh my gosh, they're\nnot quite paying attention.\""},{"time":247039,"text":"So he says, \"Can I get an amen?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":248640,"text":"Audience: Amen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249626,"text":"Chris Emdin: So I can I get an amen?\nAudience: Amen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251925,"text":"CE: And all of a sudden, everybody's reawoken."},{"time":255257,"text":"That preacher bangs on the pulpit for attention."},{"time":257318,"text":"He drops his voice at a very, very low volume"},{"time":259978,"text":"when he wants people to key into him,"},{"time":261852,"text":"and those things are the skills that we need"},{"time":264108,"text":"for the most engaging teachers."},{"time":266183,"text":"So why does teacher education"},{"time":267621,"text":"only give you theory and theory"},{"time":269694,"text":"and tell you about standards and tell you about"},{"time":271930,"text":"all of these things that have nothing to do"},{"time":273874,"text":"with the basic skills, that magic that you need"},{"time":277190,"text":"to engage an audience, to engage a student?"},{"time":280159,"text":"So I make the argument that\nwe reframe teacher education,"},{"time":283177,"text":"that we could focus on content, and that's fine,"},{"time":285962,"text":"and we could focus on theories, and that's fine,"},{"time":288268,"text":"but content and theories"},{"time":289839,"text":"with the absence of the magic"},{"time":292443,"text":"of teaching and learning means nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295354,"text":"Now people oftentimes say,\n\"Well, magic is just magic.\""},{"time":298109,"text":"There are teachers who,"},{"time":299490,"text":"despite all their challenges, who have those skills,"},{"time":301954,"text":"get into those schools and are \nable to engage an audience,"},{"time":304675,"text":"and the administrator walks by and says,"},{"time":305969,"text":"\"Wow, he's so good, I wish all\nmy teachers could be that good.\""},{"time":308897,"text":"And when they try to describe what that is,"},{"time":310940,"text":"they just say, \"He has that magic.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":313170,"text":"But I'm here to tell you"},{"time":314432,"text":"that magic can be taught."},{"time":316890,"text":"Magic can be taught."},{"time":319237,"text":"Magic can be taught."},{"time":322049,"text":"Now, how do you teach it?"},{"time":323580,"text":"You teach it by allowing people"},{"time":325251,"text":"to go into those spaces"},{"time":326656,"text":"where the magic is happening."},{"time":328258,"text":"If you want to be an aspiring\nteacher in urban education,"},{"time":330990,"text":"you've got to leave the confines of that university"},{"time":333272,"text":"and go into the hood."},{"time":335030,"text":"You've got to go in there and\nhang out at the barbershop,"},{"time":337140,"text":"you've got to attend that black church,"},{"time":338522,"text":"and you've got to view those folks"},{"time":339977,"text":"that have the power to engage"},{"time":341780,"text":"and just take notes on what they do."},{"time":343560,"text":"At our teacher education classes at my university,"},{"time":346560,"text":"I've started a project where every single student"},{"time":348954,"text":"that comes in there sits and watches rap concerts."},{"time":353546,"text":"They watch the way that the rappers move"},{"time":355769,"text":"and talk with their hands."},{"time":357302,"text":"They study the way that he\nwalks proudly across that stage."},{"time":360282,"text":"They listen to his metaphors and analogies,"},{"time":362488,"text":"and they start learning these little things"},{"time":364100,"text":"that if they practice enough"},{"time":365900,"text":"becomes the key to magic."},{"time":367589,"text":"They learn that if you just stare at a student"},{"time":369850,"text":"and raise your eyebrow about a quarter of an inch,"},{"time":372353,"text":"you don't have to say a word"},{"time":373820,"text":"because they know that that\nmeans that you want more."},{"time":377393,"text":"And if we could transform teacher education"},{"time":379848,"text":"to focus on teaching teachers"},{"time":382110,"text":"how to create that magic"},{"time":384063,"text":"then poof! we could make dead classes come alive,"},{"time":387860,"text":"we could reignite imaginations,"},{"time":389574,"text":"and we can change education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391290,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394384,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}